    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Mauga charges into the middle of a fight with Cardiac Overdrive active, using the lifesteal from his dual miniguns to out-sustain the enemy front line while Berserker denies incoming crowd control.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Berserker only protects him during the ultimate window; outside of it he has no barrier and no mobility tool, so a coordinated burst combo before he engages can drop him quickly.</p>"
